Hey ya'll! You probably got some invitations today from staff to like two different facebook groups:

1. Cru Winter Conference
2. Cru Winter Conference /// Minneapolis

The name of all winter conferences around the country are now changing to Cru Winter Conference and we're really excited about it :) Here's the link to the website, for those of you who love winter conference (and basically all things conferences), check it out--AND YOU COULD EVEN REGISTER NOW IF YOU WANT!
